flowchart TD
    A([Push or PR]) --> B[Checkout + Setup Node 20]
    B --> C[Install deps + cache]
    C --> D[Lint + Unit Tests + Coverage]
    D --> E{Coverage >= 70%?}
    E -- No --> X1([FAIL])
    E -- Yes --> F[Gitleaks BLOCKING]
    F --> G{Secrets?}
    G -- Yes --> X1
    G -- No --> H[Semgrep SAST BLOCKING]
    H --> I{High or Critical?}
    I -- Yes --> X1
    I -- No --> J[SonarCloud BLOCKING]
    J --> K{Quality Gate?}
    K -- Fail --> X1
    K -- Pass --> L[Trivy SCA and npm audit BLOCKING]
    L --> M{Critical CVE?}
    M -- Yes --> X1
    M -- No --> N[Build Docker Image]
    N --> O[Hadolint BLOCKING]
    O --> P{Lint errors?}
    P -- Yes --> X1
    P -- No --> Q[Trivy Image Scan BLOCKING]
    Q --> R{Critical CVE?}
    R -- Yes --> X1
    R -- No --> S[Syft SBOM]
    S --> T[Cosign keyless sign and attest]
    T --> U[Conftest OPA policies BLOCKING]
    U --> V{Policy violation?}
    V -- Yes --> X1
    V -- No --> W[Push to ECR and GHCR]
    W --> Y[Terraform plan and tfsec]
    Y --> YY{IaC issues?}
    YY -- Yes --> X1
    YY -- No --> Z[Deploy to ECS Fargate]
    Z --> AA[Health Check ALB]
    AA --> BB{Healthy?}
    BB -- No --> X2([Auto-rollback])
    BB -- Yes --> CC[OWASP ZAP baseline]
    CC --> DD[Push metrics to Prometheus]
    DD --> EE[Cosign verify signature]
    EE --> FF[Post summary to PR]
    FF --> GG([SUCCESS])
